original_title: Arrival: The Next Chapter Of OPM
overview: The future of the local music industry has arrived, headlined by the new chapter of OPM musicians: Lyca Gairanod, Jona Soquite, Jehramae Trangia, Because, Deny, Claudia Barretto, Just Hush, Magnus Haven, Litz and Alamat. By acclaimed concert director Paulo Valenciano.
title: Arrival: The Next Chapter Of OPM
